column2: Lipidomic Analysis of Adipose Tissue in DGAT1/DGAT2 Double Knockout Mice
This study investigates lipidomic changes in inguinal white adipose tissue (iWAT) of C57BL/6 mice lacking DGAT1 and DGAT2 enzymes (ADGAT-DKO) compared to wild-type (WT) controls.
The dataset includes 4 WT, 4 ADGAT-DKO, and 4 BQC samples, analyzed using LC-MS/MS to assess lipid profiles.
